<head>EVEN IF</head>
    <list type="altnames">
<item>ALTHOUGH</item>
<item>REGARDLESS</item>
    </list>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">雖然</item>
        <item xml:lang="och">雖</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>IF S1, NONETHELESS S2</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Suī 雖 makes hypothetical conditional clauses "it may be the case that, but....".</p>
<p>2. Zòng 縱 makes presuppositional conditional clauses "although it is admittedly the case that...".</p>
        </div>
